#: ../../source/sell.rst:2
msgid "卖出/沽空poption"
msgstr "sell/short poption"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:4
msgid ""
"在poption中，对于任意一个可以买入的收益曲线我们都可以卖出/沽空它。如果我们拥有一个 "
"poption，我们可以卖出它并直接获得底层资产。如果我们沽空一个 "
"poption，我们则需要先将一些底层资产铸造成poption，然后再沽空。具体的原理可以参考 :ref:`trade_tool` 。"
msgstr ""
"In a poption, we can sell/short any poption curve as long as we can buy it. "
"If we own a poption, we can sell it and get the underlying asset directly. "
"If we want to do a 'naked short', we need to mint poption from underlying assets first. "
"Read :ref:`trade_tool` to learn more about trading."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:9
msgid ""
"卖出一个牛市价差策略的poption，红色是当前状态，绿色是交易后的状态，两种颜色不重叠的部分就是需要从做市商处交换的 poption 。 "
"在完成交易后我们可以把绿色部分燃烧获得底层资产。这个交易最终表现为卖出poption获得底层资产。"
msgstr ""
"Sell a poption, red area is the current payoff, green area is the payoff after transaction, the disjoint part of the two colors is the poption that needs to be swaped with market maker. "
"After the swap we can burn the green area to release the underlying asset. This transaction can be expressed as selling the poption to get the underlying asset."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:15
msgid ""
"沽空同一个牛市价差策略的poption，红色是当前状态，绿色是交易后的状态，两种颜色不重叠的部分就是需要从做市商处交换的 poption "
"。可以看到需要交换的 poption 和 前一张图中的是一样的。 由于我们不持有 poption，在交易前我们需要先使用底层资产铸造所需的 "
"poption。这个交易最终表现为支付付底层资产买入沽空的 poption。"
msgstr ""
"Naked short the same poption, red area is the current payoff, green area is the payoff after transaction, the disjoint part of the two colors is the poption that needs to be swaped with market maker. "
"It is exactly the same in the previous figure."
"We need to mint the red area with some underlying asset before the transaction. This transaction can be expressed as the buying poption with the underlying asset."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:20
msgid "沽空一个看涨期权"
msgstr "Short call"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:21
msgid "在期权小工具的设置中将share设为负数就能沽空相应期权："
msgstr ""
"Set the share as a negative number to short the option in option tool widget:"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:26
msgid "下图是对应的收益函数，因为我们是在沽空，因此收益函数也在负区间，此时的cost也是负数，实质表示的是我们卖出poption收益曲线并买入底层资产："
msgstr ""
"The following chart is the payoff function. Because we are shorting, the payoff function is in the negative domain, and the cost is also a negative number,"
" which actrually means we are selling the poption and buying the underlying asset."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:31
msgid ""
"在结算信息中，我们也能看到在这里等价成本变为了负数，当我们拥有此资产时，完成交易后我们能获得相应的回报。如果我们没有相应的资产，我们放入一定的底层资产去实现裸卖空，值得注意的是在poption中裸卖空采用的是和买多一样的机制，因此也同样没有清算风险。详见"
" :ref:`trade_tool` ："
msgstr ""
"In the trade card, the equivalent cost here also becomes negative. If we sell the poption, we get the underlying asset. "
"If we don't have the poption, we shall use the underlying assets to mint some first. "
"It is worth to notice that in poption the naked shorting uses the exactly same mechanism as longing, so there is no liquidation risk as well. "
"Read :ref:`trade_tool` to learn more."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:37
msgid "沽空一个无常损失"
msgstr "Short impermanent loss"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:38
msgid "我们在无常损失工具中输入负数就可以沽空无常损失。具体可以参考下图例子中的方法："
msgstr ""
"We can short the impermanent loss by entering a negative number in the impermanent loss hedging tool. Follow the figures below to get the detail."

#: ../../source/sell.rst:50
msgid "卖出所有持有的poption"
msgstr "Sell all poption"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:51
msgid "在 SALE 工具中点击 SELL 我们可以生成一个卖出所有所持有的poption收益曲线的交易。如下图所示："
msgstr ""
"Click on SELL button in the selling tool we can generate a transaction to sell all of the poption in the current address. "

#: ../../source/sell.rst:57
msgid "讨论"
msgstr "Discussion"

#: ../../source/sell.rst:58
msgid "我们可以看到在poption中沽空一个衍生品非常的方便，这有助与市场价格机制充分发挥作用，及时准确传递市场信号，满足各种金融需求。此外在poption中沽空也是安全的，无清算风险的。"
msgstr ""
"We can see that it is very convenient to short a derivative in poption, which helps the market to play its role to give  "
"" accurate price signals and meet various financial needs. "
"In addition, shorting in poption is safe and free of liquidation risk."

